sub_title: Managing Director @ Chemistry Team (Amsterdam & Singapore) | Designing meaningful customer centric solutions for complex organisations
summary:
I am a passionate practitioner of human-centred design. In my work, I have regularly seen how technology, processes, and even policies override the human benefit that they had set out to achieve in the first place.

With over 20 years of experience, I have had the privilege to work with a broad spectrum of government agencies as well as some of the biggest brands like Visa, Dell, and GE Healthcare to bring about meaningful change through carefully crafted solutions.
